text: Bruna Rossi (born 15 July 1948) is a retired Italian diver. She competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics in the 10 m platform and finished in 21st place. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic divers of Italy Category:Divers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Italian female divers
